
This port is meant to build and provide a full installation of DTC using
courier -imap, -pop3, -maildrop, including all dependencies required to use it.
This isn't the only possible configuration of applications to run with it, see
the main port, dtc-toaster and dtc-cyrus for the various apps that can be used.

WWW: http://www.gplhost.com/software-dtc.html
